      "updated": 1780930115480,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Stuff I am showing:\n    - may or may not align directly with \"how you do things\". \n        - jeff could be wrong. If you think that is the case, bring it up.\n        - Your team could be using outdated practices - pre \"devops\" stuff. No problem. But don't discount what I'm saying.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Stuff I am showing:\n    - may or may not align directly with \"how you do things\". \n        - jeff could be wrong. If you think that is the case, bring it up.\n        - Your team could be using outdated practices - pre \"devops\" stuff. No problem. But don't discount what I'm saying.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "pJG4Fj7vfGWZJRu3k7LVm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 263,
      "y": 355,
      "width": 953.0393676757812,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
