      "seed": 1785600148,
      "version": 347,
      "versionNonce": 1727489940,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780930233189,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\"Cloud Native\" - write your code in a way that it can be run anywhere - on prem, in the cloud, etc.\n    - don't write code that can ONLY run on-prem, or only on AWS, or only on Azure, etc.\n    - This is a \"default stance\" - you can have exceptions, but this is the default.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\"Cloud Native\" - write your code in a way that it can be run anywhere - on prem, in the cloud, etc.\n    - don't write code that can ONLY run on-prem, or only on AWS, or only on Azure, etc.\n    - This is a \"default stance\" - you can have exceptions, but this is the default.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "iU9_jTNQX2BsNLtVEXBVO",
