      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": ".Net Core - API\n    - You get a web server for free.\n    - Each API you create is a web server (Kestrel)\n    - You just add your special sauce.\n    - 12 Factor App: \"Port Binding\"",
